<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:08:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>普京再次警告：“如果……俄罗斯准备使用核武器”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapon-if-putin-warns-again/articleshow/108471757.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108471757.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京重申准备使用核武器来保护主权。他强调需要与北约盟国和乌克兰进行认真讨论。普京提到了扰乱俄罗斯总统选举的行为，并谴责乌克兰在俄罗斯境内发动的袭击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapon-if-putin-warns-again/articleshow/108471757.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过禁止 TikTok 法案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-house-passes-bill-to-ban-tiktok/articleshow/108470610.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108470610.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:47:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-house-passes-bill-to-ban-tiktok/articleshow/108470610.cms</guid></item><item><title>连续数周的大雪和降雨造成至少 60 名阿富汗人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/at-least-60-afghans-killed-by-weeks-of-intense-snow-rain/articleshow/108467889.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108467889.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据阿富汗灾害部称，过去三周，阿富汗的大雨和大雪已夺去了至少60人的生命。尽管冬季干燥，但每年的这个时候通常会带来危险的天气，例如洪水，给社区造成严重破坏。贾南·萨耶克说：“不幸的是，由于雨雪天气，我们失去了60名同胞，23人受伤。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/at-least-60-afghans-killed-by-weeks-of-intense-snow-rain/articleshow/108467889.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国考虑向自愿移居卢旺达的移民支付费用</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-mulls-plan-to-pay-migrants-to-move-to-rwanda-voluntarily/articleshow/108465234.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108465234.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国政府周三表示，正在考虑一项计划，将被拒绝的寻求庇护者自愿送往卢旺达，据报道，英国政府将向他们支付高达 3,000 英镑（3,800 美元）的费用。该计划是现有自愿遣返安排的延伸，出台之际，部长们正在努力启动单独的有争议的提案，将其他移民驱逐到这个东非国家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:01:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-mulls-plan-to-pay-migrants-to-move-to-rwanda-voluntarily/articleshow/108465234.cms</guid></item><item><title>“对纳瓦尔尼助手的袭击可能是俄罗斯组织的”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/education/times-study-abroad/europe/assault-on-navalny-aide-likely-organised-by-russia-says-lithuanian-counter-intelligence/articleshow/108463817.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108463817.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的重要助手列昂尼德·沃尔科夫在立陶宛遭到袭击。这次袭击由俄罗斯策划，使用了催泪瓦斯和锤子。此次袭击可能与俄罗斯总统选举有关。沃尔科夫在 Telegram 上发布了他受伤和车辆损坏的照片。调查正在进行中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/education/times-study-abroad/europe/assault-on-navalny-aide-likely-organised-by-russia-says-lithuanian-counter-intelligence/articleshow/108463817.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔总理普拉昌达赢得议会信任投票</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/nepal-pm-prachanda-wins-vote-of-confidence-in-parliament/articleshow/108464217.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108464217.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/nepal-pm-prachanda-wins-vote-of-confidence-in-parliament/articleshow/108464217.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国暂停向联合国巴勒斯坦救援机构提供资金可能会永久暂停</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-pause-on-funding-un-relief-agency-for-palestinians-may-become-permanent/articleshow/108462857.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108462857.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-pause-on-funding-un-relief-agency-for-palestinians-may-become-permanent/articleshow/108462857.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰争议后，教皇再次谴责“战争的疯狂”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/after-ukraine-controversy-pope-again-condemns-madness-of-war/articleshow/108461796.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108461796.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/after-ukraine-controversy-pope-again-condemns-madness-of-war/articleshow/108461796.cms</guid></item><item><title>无人机袭击俄罗斯炼油厂，多人受伤：州长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/drone-strike-hits-russia-oil-refinery-several-wounded-governor/articleshow/108460488.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108460488.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;无人机对俄罗斯炼油厂的袭击已连续第二天持续。乌克兰发动重大袭击，袭击了下诺夫哥罗德附近的主要炼油厂。据报道，袭击中发生了火灾和人员伤亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/drone-strike-hits-russia-oil-refinery-several-wounded-governor/articleshow/108460488.cms</guid></item><item><title>援助组织称因从事间谍活动而被俄罗斯拘留的韩国人从事人道主义工作</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-held-in-russia-for-spying-did-humanitarian-work-aid-group-says/articleshow/108465513.cms</link><description>韩国传教士白光淳因间谍罪在俄罗斯被捕，导致俄韩关系紧张。白的援助组织否认了这些指控，并表示他正在从事人道主义工作。韩国正在与俄罗斯就白克的释放进行沟通。由于莫斯科与朝鲜关系日益密切，俄罗斯和韩国之间的关系日益紧张。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:11:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-held-in-russia-for-spying-did-humanitarian-work-aid-group-says/articleshow/108465513.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京：俄罗斯核武库优于美国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-russian-nuclear-arsenal-better-than-that-of-us/articleshow/108459948.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108459948.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普京重申，愿意通过核冲突来保护国家地位。核能力优越。警告乌克兰介入的后果。愿意进行谈判，但要求安全保证。即将举行的选举因乌克兰无人机袭击而中断，俄罗斯的袭击造成人员伤亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:38:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-russian-nuclear-arsenal-better-than-that-of-us/articleshow/108459948.cms</guid></item><item><title>纳瓦尔尼的助手列昂尼德·沃尔科夫在袭击后回国，立陶宛警方展开调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/navalnys-aide-leonid-volkov-returns-home-after-attack-lithuania-police-launch-investigation/articleshow/108458563.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108458563.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;立陶宛警方周三表示，他们已对已故俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的前参谋长、长期助手列昂尼德·沃尔科夫周二在维尔纽斯住所外遭到袭击后发起调查。沃尔科夫在 Telegram 帖子中表示，他在接受治疗后于周三从医院回到家中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/navalnys-aide-leonid-volkov-returns-home-after-attack-lithuania-police-launch-investigation/articleshow/108458563.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙船只正在前往加沙，运送急需的援助</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/spanish-ship-en-route-to-gaza-with-desperately-needed-aid/articleshow/108454860.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108454860.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一艘西班牙援助船正通过一条新的海上走廊前往加沙，运送急需的粮食供应。斋月之前长达数周的停火外交努力失败了。新的轰炸仍在继续，加剧了人道主义危机。国际社会正在寻求替代的援助运送路线，包括空投和第二艘船只。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/spanish-ship-en-route-to-gaza-with-desperately-needed-aid/articleshow/108454860.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯袭击乌克兰东部地区苏梅和顿涅茨克，造成两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/two-killed-in-russian-attacks-on-ukraines-eastern-regions-sumy-and-donetsk/articleshow/108458391.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108458391.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当地州长瓦迪姆·菲拉什金 (Vadym Filashkin) 在 Telegram 消息应用程序上表示，俄罗斯人在顿涅茨克地区米尔诺赫拉德镇投下一枚炸弹，造成两人死亡、五人受伤。苏梅地区军事管理局表示，一架俄罗斯无人机夜间袭击了一座公寓楼，造成人员伤亡。政府表示，一栋五层住宅楼的 30 套公寓遭到破坏，其中 15 套大部分被毁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/two-killed-in-russian-attacks-on-ukraines-eastern-regions-sumy-and-donetsk/articleshow/108458391.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局的韦伯和哈勃望远镜证实了宇宙膨胀，加深了天文之谜</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nasas-webb-and-hubble-telescopes-confirm-cosmic-expansion-deepen-astronomical-mystery/articleshow/108456624.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108456624.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈勃张力是宇宙学中的一个谜题，它产生于观测到的宇宙膨胀速率与预期速率的差异。哈勃和詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜之间的合作消除了测量误差，并暗示了涉及暗能量的潜在误解。未来的观测旨在弥合宇宙的起源和当前状态之间的差距。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:06:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nasas-webb-and-hubble-telescopes-confirm-cosmic-expansion-deepen-astronomical-mystery/articleshow/108456624.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京：俄罗斯已做好应对核战争威胁的准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-nuclear-war-vladimir-putin-interview-ukraine-war-us-nuclear-weapons-russian-election/articleshow/108452374.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108452374.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京保证，如果其主权受到威胁，该国已做好应对核战争的充分准备，但强调目前的局势并不需要采取如此极端的措施。普京强调了在俄罗斯领土或乌克兰部署美国军队的后果，并表示俄罗斯将认为这是一种干预。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-nuclear-war-vladimir-putin-interview-ukraine-war-us-nuclear-weapons-russian-election/articleshow/108452374.cms</guid></item><item><title>印尼苏拉威西岛一艘渔船倾覆 造成2人死亡24人失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/2-dead-and-24-missing-after-a-fishing-boat-capsized-off-indonesias-sulawesi-island/articleshow/108456444.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108456444.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于巨浪和暴风雨天气，Dewi Jaya 2 号渔船在印度尼西亚苏拉威西岛附近倾覆。 2人死亡、24人失踪。救援人员使用充气艇进行搜寻。近年来，过度拥挤的船只和松懈的安全法规已导致数百人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/2-dead-and-24-missing-after-a-fishing-boat-capsized-off-indonesias-sulawesi-island/articleshow/108456444.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧洲世界首创的人工智能规则即将获得最终批准。接下来会发生什么</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europes-world-first-ai-rules-are-set-for-final-approval-heres-what-happens-next/articleshow/108454654.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108454654.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟立法者将批准世界领先的人工智能法案，该法案将规范人工智能并成为全球路标。该法案采用基于风险的方法并解决生成人工智能模型。 OpenAI 首席执行官 Sam Altman 表示支持该法案。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europes-world-first-ai-rules-are-set-for-final-approval-heres-what-happens-next/articleshow/108454654.cms</guid></item><item><title>官员称乌克兰无人机连续第二晚袭击俄罗斯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-drones-attack-russia-for-second-night-in-a-row-officials-say/articleshow/108453000.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108453000.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰官员周三表示，乌克兰连续第二晚对俄罗斯多个地区发动大规模无人机袭击，沃罗涅日地区上空的 30 多架无人机被摧毁。与乌克兰接壤的沃罗涅日地区州长亚历山大·古谢夫在 Telegram 消息应用程序上表示：“无人机袭击的危险仍然存在。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 05:16:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-drones-attack-russia-for-second-night-in-a-row-officials-say/articleshow/108453000.cms</guid></item><item><title>纳瓦兹·谢里夫的儿子在伦敦自我流放六年后返回巴基斯坦</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/nawaz-sharifs-sons-return-to-pakistan-after-six-years-of-self-exile-in-london/articleshow/108452079.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108452079.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 05:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/nawaz-sharifs-sons-return-to-pakistan-after-six-years-of-self-exile-in-london/articleshow/108452079.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>